name: testForPartiallyPaidTransferInCancelledStatus()

testSteps.description: Read random data from DB2: data about external firm transfers (to EJ account) with 'Cancelled' status and partially paid

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select
    transfer.br_no, transfer.cust_no, transfer.CRE_DA,
    transfer.EDJ_STAT_CD, transfer.PREV_EDJ_STAT_CD,
    transfer.TFR_TYPE_CD,
    transfer.TOT_MKT_VAL_AMT,
    transfer.TFR_IN_OUT_CD,
    transfer.FIRM_KEY, transfer.INSTR_ID, transfer.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID,
    transfer.FIRM_TY_CD, transfer.INHRT_IRA_IND,
    firm.FIRM_NA, outside_account.OUTSIDE_ACCT_NO

    from PROD.TFR_RQST_10327  as transfer
    join PROD.OUTSIDE_FIRM_10460 as firm on firm.FIRM_KEY = transfer.FIRM_KEY
    join PROD.OUTSIDE_ACCT_10136 as outside_account on outside_account.TFR_KEY = transfer.TFR_KEY

    where
    br_no=4454
    and TFR_IN_OUT_CD = 'I' -- to EJ account
    and EDJ_STAT_CD = '07' --table TFR_EDJ_ST_10329 contains description, 8 - branch action, A CODE THAT IDENTIFIES THAT JONES STATUS FOR A TRANSFER VALID VALUES ARE: 01 - 11. INCOMPLETE (01) INTRANSIT (02) INPROCESS (03) PENDING (04) COMPLETED (05) REJECTED (06) CANCELLED (07) BRANCHPROC (08) BRANCHCOMP (09) RESIDUAL (10) RESCOMPLT (11)
    and CRE_DA > '2024-10-06'
    and ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID = 309
    --    and FIRM_TY_CD = 'MFD' --amount = MFD - mutual funds
    --    and FIRM_TY_CD <> 'MFD' and TFR_PROC_CD = 'RCR' -- residual
    --    and FIRM_TY_CD <> 'MFD' and TFR_PROC_CD <> 'RCR' and TFR_TYPE_CD = '1' --full
        and FIRM_TY_CD <> 'MFD' and TFR_PROC_CD <> 'RCR' and TFR_TYPE_CD = '2' --partial
    FETCH FIRST 50 ROWS ONLY

reportData.title: SQL result

children.description: Get EJ account ID by account customer number 44517023

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select sub_acc.ACCT_ID as ACCT_ID
from PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc
where sub_acc.VNDR_ACCT_ID = '44517023'

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select
rlt.RLTSHP_ID
from PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc
join PROD.RLTSHP_13120 as rlt on rlt.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID = acctgrp.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID
join PROD.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_DTL_13088 as acctgrp on acctgrp.ACCT_ID=sub_acc.ACCT_ID
where
sub_acc.ACCT_ID = 128913864
